@startuml Supra_Admin_Actor_Diagram
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE

title Supra Admin Portal — Actor Hierarchy & Role Definitions

left to right direction

actor "Platform Super Admin\n(super_admin)" as SA #LightGreen
actor "Platform Admin\n(platform_admin)" as PA #LightBlue
actor "Platform Support\n(platform_support)" as PS #LightYellow
actor "Platform Billing\n(platform_billing)" as PB #LightCoral
actor "Platform Analyst\n(platform_analyst)" as PAnalyst #Lavender
actor "Platform Developer\n(platform_developer)" as PD #LightGray

note right of SA
  **Full Access (wildcard *)**
  All permissions across
  the Supra Admin Portal
end note

note right of PA
  **Full Operational Access**
  Tenants, Billing, Users,
  System, ERP, Access Control
  (except Super Admin assignment)
end note

note right of PS
  **Support Focus**
  View tenants, support tickets,
  analytics, notifications
end note

note right of PB
  **Finance Focus**
  Billing, invoices, payments,
  subscriptions, revenue analytics
end note

note right of PAnalyst
  **Data & Reports Focus**
  Analytics, audit logs,
  tenant usage, revenue reports
end note

note right of PD
  **Technical Focus**
  System config, templates,
  infrastructure, debug
end note

SA -[#green,bold]- PA : generalizes
SA -[#green,bold]- PS : generalizes
SA -[#green,bold]- PB : generalizes
SA -[#green,bold]- PAnalyst : generalizes
SA -[#green,bold]- PD : generalizes

@enduml
